            "title": "黑期升233點   ADR高水140點  滙控阿里高水",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期升233點或0.91%，報25746。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨天收市高水140點或0.55%，報25671點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"滙豐銀行。巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_CR_source-BP_HSBC_01.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"滙豐銀行。巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_CR_source-BP_HSBC_01.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">滙豐銀行。巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報117.1元，較香港收市價高2.7% ; 阿里巴巴(09988) ADR折合港元計收報152.62元，較香港收市價高1.3% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣78.07元，較香港收市價高水1% ; 三大股份ADR成推升動力。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700) ADR折合港元計收報604.33元，較香港收市價0.5% ; 小米(01810) ADR折合港元計收報42.41元，較香港收市價0.5% ; 網易(09999) ADR折合港元計收報212.02元，較香港收市價高1.2% ;  </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\"> 港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣403.41元，較香港收市價高0.7% ; 恒生(00011) ADR折合港元計收報148.87元，較香港收市價低水2.7%</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥明生物(02269) ADR折合港元計收報32.49元，較香港收市價低水3% ;石藥(01093) ADR折合港元計收報7.61元，較香港收市價低水1.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報25788點，升218點，較昨日恒指收市25530點，高水257點，成交14561張。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國指夜市期指收報9014點，較昨日國指收市高水80點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15501303-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%8d%87233%e9%bb%9e-adr%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4140%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-12 08:55:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "道指升646點　與標指齊創新高　甲骨文重挫近11%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股個別發展。道瓊斯工業平均指數與標準普爾500指數創新高，市場憧憬美國明年減息或多於一次。甲骨文股價顯著下挫，拖累納斯達克指數下跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250124_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股。AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250124_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股。AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數高開25點後，升幅擴大至最多698點，衝上48756點，收市報48704點，升646點，升幅1.34%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數升穿6900點，報6901點，升14點，升幅0.21%，曾跌0.77%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數曾跌近1.5%，之後收復大部分失地，收報23593點，跌60點，跌幅0.25%，一度滑落1.46%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">甲骨文業績差過預期，並估計全年度資本開支達500億美元，較上季預測高150億美元，股價收市插水10.8%，為2001年以來最傷，市值蒸發逾千億美元；股價一度跌逾16%，收市跌近11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝達(Nvidia)股價挫1.6%。蘋果公司供應商博通(Broadcom)周四收市後公布業績，股價挫1.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他大型科技股遍向下，Tesla及Nvidia跌1%或以上。亞馬遜跌逾0.6%。Meta靠穩。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">迪士尼宣布向OpenAI投資10億美元，並已經達成內容授權協議，股價漲2.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">禮來(Eli Lilly)一隻研發中的減肥藥初步療效理想，股價升1.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Visa獲美銀唱好，股價急漲6.1%，為表現最強道指成份股；美國運通和高盛都升2.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15501191-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87646%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%80%e8%88%87%e6%a8%99%e6%8c%87%e9%bd%8a%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e3%80%80%e7%94%b2%e9%aa%a8%e6%96%87%e9%87%8d%e6%8c%ab%e8%bf%9111",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250802_GL_source-AP_WallSt_02.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-12 08:40:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價低收1.5%　關注俄烏和平談判及美國庫存",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原油期貨價格跌約1.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/OIL-PRICE_FB_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/OIL-PRICE_FB_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶61.28美元，下跌93美仙，跌幅1.49%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報每桶57.6美元，下跌86美仙，跌幅1.47%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">投資者繼續關注俄烏和平談判進展，另外亦擔心美國汽油及柴油庫增加。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15501214-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b61-5%e3%80%80%e9%97%9c%e6%b3%a8%e4%bf%84%e7%83%8f%e5%92%8c%e5%b9%b3%e8%ab%87%e5%88%a4%e5%8f%8a%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%ba%ab%e5%ad%98",
