        {
            "title": "歐股向好   法股升近0.8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市上升，投資者預計美國明年減息或多於一次，另外評估瑞士央行的政策決定。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市反彈0.55%，報581點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數收報9703點，升47點，升幅0.49%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報8085點，升63點，升幅0.79%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報24294點，升164點，升幅0.68%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報43702點，升0.54%或236點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報16883點，升0.72%或120點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15501179-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e5%90%91%e5%a5%bd-%e6%b3%95%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%910-8",
